\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {4}{\ignorespaces Event-study estimates for four BFS series. Each panel plots the interaction coefficient between AI exposure and a month-relative-to-November-2022 indicator. BA = total applications; CBA = corrected applications; HBA = high-propensity applications; WBA = applications with planned wages; BF4Q/BF8Q = formations within 4/8 quarters; PBF4Q/PBF8Q = projected formations; SBF4Q/SBF8Q = seasonally-adjusted formations; DUR4Q/DUR8Q = median weeks to formation (levels, not logs). Shaded bands are 95\,\% confidence intervals based on sector-clustered standard errors. All specifications include sector and month fixed effects. Dashed vertical line marks November 2022 ($t=0$).}}{13}{figure.caption.11}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:es_robust}{{4}{13}{Event-study estimates for four BFS series. Each panel plots the interaction coefficient between AI exposure and a month-relative-to-November-2022 indicator. BA = total applications; CBA = corrected applications; HBA = high-propensity applications; WBA = applications with planned wages; BF4Q/BF8Q = formations within 4/8 quarters; PBF4Q/PBF8Q = projected formations; SBF4Q/SBF8Q = seasonally-adjusted formations; DUR4Q/DUR8Q = median weeks to formation (levels, not logs). Shaded bands are 95\,\% confidence intervals based on sector-clustered standard errors. All specifications include sector and month fixed effects. Dashed vertical line marks November 2022 ($t=0$)}{figure.caption.11}{}}
